  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0da9\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a \u0dbd\u0dda\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A letter from the Inspector General of Police to the Secretary of Defense about an act of vandalism",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tomorrow (05) or tomorrow (06) on the occasion of the 'Black Tiger Celebration', a bomb attack, some sabotage will be carried out targeting the northern, eastern or southern province. T. T. e. Inspector General of Police C. D. Mr. Wickramaratne has sent a letter to Defense Secretary retired General Kamal Gunaratne and informed.",
        "In this article, it is stated that the relevant attack will be carried out by a group of members of a foreign intelligence service.",
        "Due to this, it is also mentioned in the letter that some notice has already been given to the personnel and dignitaries working in foreign institutions in the Jaffna area not to participate in any event during these two days.",
        "In the meantime, the Inspector General of Police has reported to him that the Janata Vimukthi Peramuna and frontline parties and opposition groups are planning to target local councilors and politicians and attack them and their homes in the future to put pressure on the government and embarrass the government. This article informed.",
        "Based on information from the Anti-Terrorism and Investigation Division, the Inspector General of Police forwarded this letter to the Defense Secretary on the 27th."
      ],
